      "description": "Looking for a cheap, honest set of wheels that won\u2019t break the bank? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and can still be a great little runaround, first car, or project for someone handy. If you want basic, affordable transport with a price that leaves room in the budget, this one is well worth a look. Come check it out and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you.",
